data.description: Looking for an affordable home needing a little TLC that boasts options to offset your mortgage, build an investment portfolio or supply a canvas for with an opportunity to gain a big boost in equity? This home offers all of that & more! Boasting eye-catching curb appeal outside & original charming features inside (think arched entryways, original hardwood floors, etc) this listing is sure to hit your must-see list. Buyers will love the well-planned design; offering the option to reside in it as a single family residence or rent out the basement for an income producing opportunity (it even offers a private entrance for tenants). Offering an abundance of natural light streaming through the large updated windows on the main level & well-stocked with a set of appliances (including the washer & dryer) this home is inviting & ready for its' new owners. Outside features a large fenced yard with mature trees, an empty chicken coop - waiting to be occupied & a single car attached garage. Even more, this home sits in a desirable location, with quick, easy access to local schools & frequented parks. This opportunity is a fantastic find, tucked in the heart of Idaho Falls in a quiet, friendly neighborhood this residence is a perfect ticket to making home ownership your reality.
